// Example 01: Hello — bare markup, no state, no logic.
// Demonstrates the three closer forms: explicit </tag>, trailing /, and bare /.

<program>

<div>
  <h1>Hello, scrml</>
  <p>Three ways to close a tag: explicit, trailing, or bare.</p>
  <footer>No framework. Just output.
  </>
</>

</program>
